## Patterns across rejections

- [Cross-cutting pattern, e.g., "Two of three rejections were at tech screen, not resume screen — past the resume bar, not past execution-under-time-pressure bar."]
- [Recurring theme across companies, e.g., "Ambiguity navigation + metric ownership — same themes will show up at the next staff-level loop."]
- [Filter-type vs. skill-type rejections — separate them so you don't over-drill on things that weren't real signals.]
